            Whether you're a startup or an established brand, our custom-built AI solutions learn from your business needs and deliver responses that feel natural, personal, and on-brand — 24/7.
          </p>

          <div style="background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-primary); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px;">💡 What We Offer:</h3>
