        </div>
        <h2 class="newsletter-title">Stay Ahead with AI Insights</h2>
        <p class="newsletter-subtitle">
          Get weekly tips, product updates, and exclusive content on AI-powered customer support delivered straight to your inbox. No spam, just value.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="subscription-card">
        <h3 class="form-title">📬 Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h3>
